title: Gh pages v2
Add TypeForm Application
body:
Check it out and lemme know what you think or if something needs to be changed.
- If you just click on `index.html` and try to load the typeform it wont work. The site's files needs to be served from a server.
- Make sure you have python installed and run the following command from the root directory of the project:

``` python
python -m SimpleHTTPServer 8000
```
- this will serve the files at http://localhost:8000/
